Oral Care Mouthwash for Kids: A gentle, non-spicy xylitol mouthwash suited for newborns and toddlers which has a favorability rating of 99.9%. oh care Mouthwash has P113+ antimicrobial peptide that efficiently keeps your kids' teeth and gums healthy.

This total care mouthwash for kids is 11.8 fl oz and is used daily in the morning, evening, and after meals, along with other oh care products, to prevent cavities in your child's teeth before they happen.
